# internal/ dogfood workspace — mirrors the agent-memory/ patterns above.
# The refactor moved dogfood from root agent-memory/ to internal/agent-memory/,
# but the root patterns above only match root-level paths, not internal/ paths.
# These mirrored patterns keep generated dogfood artifacts out of git while
# preserving the "latest" snapshot files as tracked dogfood evidence.
